query:
SELECT e.id, e.name, e.code, e.role, e.branchId, b.name as branchName 
FROM employees e 
LEFT JOIN branches b ON e.branchId = b.id 
WHERE e.name LIKE '%السيد%' OR e.name LIKE '%سيد%'
